WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.847
=Episode 6=

01:38.704 --> 01:42.424
My grandfather encouraged his students
to learn about current affairs.

01:43.463 --> 01:44.263
Is that so?

01:44.864 --> 01:46.144
What did he teach?

01:46.543 --> 01:50.024
My grandfather and tutors annotated
the Treatise on Rivers and Waterways.

01:50.823 --> 01:52.463
They often talked

01:52.463 --> 01:54.103
about your waterway reform.

01:54.664 --> 01:57.383
The reform made 30,000 trackers
exempt from conscription.

01:57.823 --> 01:59.463
And four-tenths of the tax was waived.

01:59.704 --> 02:02.823
The tutors all praised you
as a remarkable woman of governance.

02:02.823 --> 02:03.823
They greatly admired you.

02:04.424 --> 02:06.623
Such matters reached the mountain?

02:07.823 --> 02:11.183
Even the mountain guardians
heard of your great deeds.

02:11.600 --> 02:14.704
In the third year of the Xide Era, you
allowed the unprivileged to take exams.

02:14.704 --> 02:16.503
It was an opportunity to serve at court.

02:17.063 --> 02:19.024
In the fifth year,
waterways were dredged.

02:19.503 --> 02:22.264
In early autumn,
the land tax could be levied in kind.

02:22.503 --> 02:24.704
Master Gu even made poetry
to praise you for it.

02:24.864 --> 02:27.264
Now our nation is peaceful
and prosperous.

02:27.864 --> 02:30.104
My grandfather said
it's all thanks to you, Your Majesty.

02:36.063 --> 02:36.903
Princess Ding.

02:38.544 --> 02:39.343
Yes.

02:40.304 --> 02:43.544
Your grandfather is humble,
steady, yet uncommunicative.

02:43.864 --> 02:46.824
His brilliance shines
only in state affairs.

02:47.623 --> 02:50.544
You, however, are quite eloquent,
unlike him.

02:54.984 --> 02:56.063
Your Majesty.

02:56.743 --> 02:58.384
My grandfather is a pillar of the state.

02:58.984 --> 03:00.903
I am but a humble woman.

03:01.623 --> 03:04.584
All I want is an ordinary life of peace.

03:05.783 --> 03:08.384
My praise of Your Majesty
is not flattery.

03:08.623 --> 03:10.623
We all benefit from your benevolence.

03:11.063 --> 03:12.264
Common homes find peace.

03:12.424 --> 03:13.584
Fields yield harvest.

03:13.663 --> 03:15.264
We all enjoy a profound peace.

03:16.424 --> 03:18.903
My respect for Your Majesty
comes from the heart.

03:18.903 --> 03:20.424
I admire your great feats.

03:34.984 --> 03:36.048
Thank you, Your Majesty.

03:45.663 --> 03:48.063
The grapes here are sweet and delicious.

03:52.824 --> 03:53.623
Your Majesty.

03:54.304 --> 03:58.024
I heard Prince Li composed a new piece.

03:58.024 --> 04:01.623
How about he plays for us?

04:02.783 --> 04:03.584
Permitted.

04:06.183 --> 04:08.463
My new piece is unfinished.

04:08.704 --> 04:10.984
I fear it would upset you, Your Majesty.

04:11.424 --> 04:12.864
I beg your forgiveness.

04:13.544 --> 04:17.704
Please allow me to play an old melody

04:18.103 --> 04:19.103
to liven the gathering.

04:20.303 --> 04:21.264
What is it?

04:25.624 --> 04:26.504
Green Plum Prelude.

05:01.104 --> 05:02.800
(Young Mo Jingli)

05:09.360 --> 05:10.736
(Master Yu, Lishan Academy)

05:16.663 --> 05:17.663
The fourth tremolo

05:17.903 --> 05:21.983
should sound clear and crisp.

05:23.303 --> 05:24.504
What sound was that?

05:25.064 --> 05:27.504
Sounds like a frog jumps into the pond.

05:42.983 --> 05:43.783
Your Highness!

05:49.463 --> 05:50.264
Does it hurt?

05:57.504 --> 05:59.264
Quite passionate.

06:00.024 --> 06:02.463
Prince Li poured his feelings
into the tune.

06:07.103 --> 06:08.384
I'm just not good at this.

06:15.303 --> 06:18.384
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

06:20.223 --> 06:23.064
Chiming chords require coordination.

06:23.983 --> 06:25.543
Modulating to a plaintive key

06:25.824 --> 06:29.463
only leads to a sad melody.

06:35.983 --> 06:37.783
Since the music is over,

06:38.303 --> 06:39.663
you all may leave now.

06:45.543 --> 06:46.983
- I take my leave.
- I take my leave.

06:49.303 --> 06:52.624
I wonder if the pastry shop
in the West Market is still open.

06:52.783 --> 06:56.423
Have Qingyu stop by if it is.

06:56.824 --> 06:58.103
You've been walking for long.

06:58.264 --> 06:59.504
Is that what you are thinking?

06:59.624 --> 07:00.783
What else then?

07:01.663 --> 07:03.584
Your Highness,
does your hand still hurt?

07:03.903 --> 07:05.343
Let me dress it when we're home.

07:05.343 --> 07:06.103
Your Highness.

07:13.504 --> 07:14.303
Halt!

07:14.903 --> 07:17.504
Ye Li, you're happy, aren't you?

07:17.903 --> 07:19.264
You've left the mountain

07:19.264 --> 07:20.303
and married Prince Ding.

07:20.663 --> 07:22.624
Even the Empress Dowager favors you.

07:22.903 --> 07:24.303
Her Majesty chatted with you.

07:25.264 --> 07:26.423
Her Majesty is very kind.

07:27.423 --> 07:28.584
Sure, Her Majesty is.

07:28.903 --> 07:31.303
But don't forget the sins
your kind once committed!

07:32.303 --> 07:35.024
Logically, I should call you sister.

07:35.504 --> 07:37.783
It's a matter of propriety,
and a family rule.

07:38.463 --> 07:39.624
But you don't deserve it.

07:40.103 --> 07:42.264
Lishan Academy was insolent

07:42.264 --> 07:43.384
and challenged Her Majesty,

07:43.624 --> 07:45.704
almost bringing calamity
upon the whole Ye family!

07:46.423 --> 07:49.223
Fortunately, Father decisively cut ties
with the academy

07:49.663 --> 07:52.103
and begged for mercy,
kneeling in the snow.

07:52.303 --> 07:54.504
That's how he saved the entire family.

07:54.584 --> 07:57.264
The entire family pulled together.

07:57.663 --> 08:00.783
And my mom and the ladies
managed the household well.

08:00.903 --> 08:03.064
That's why our family became prosperous.

08:03.064 --> 08:04.303
And that's why you have it all.

08:05.103 --> 08:06.264
As a big family,

08:06.663 --> 08:09.223
we're all in the same boat.

08:10.504 --> 08:12.064
Have you shown an ounce of gratitude?

08:13.384 --> 08:15.223
My mom safeguarded your dowry.

08:15.663 --> 08:18.264
My maternal uncles
managed your business tirelessly.

08:18.624 --> 08:21.463
But now you put on airs
as Princess Consort.

08:21.463 --> 08:22.663
And you stole our assets.

08:23.584 --> 08:25.663
You ranted before the Empress Dowager.

08:26.463 --> 08:29.103
Do you wish to disgrace our family
like your mom?

08:29.824 --> 08:31.064
Do you deserve your surname?

08:31.103 --> 08:32.384
Do you deserve to be my sister?

08:34.104 --> 08:35.703
Whose assets have I seized?

08:36.504 --> 08:37.823
The Ye family's.

08:38.624 --> 08:39.783
By that logic,

08:40.423 --> 08:44.264
your marriage dowry
should belong to Prince Li too.

08:45.024 --> 08:48.024
So the entertainers in his house
can also spend your money?

08:48.024 --> 08:49.744
How dare you insult my mom!

08:49.783 --> 08:51.663
One more important thing.

08:52.224 --> 08:54.783
Wh-What?

08:55.224 --> 08:56.864
You should never have called me sister.

08:57.624 --> 09:00.504
Prince Ding and Prince Li
are close relatives.

09:02.104 --> 09:04.104
You should be calling me Aunt.

09:05.783 --> 09:06.423
What?

09:06.423 --> 09:07.224
Princess Li.

09:08.783 --> 09:10.104
Prince Li is out of sight.

09:13.024 --> 09:13.903
Where is His Highness?

09:16.703 --> 09:18.984
Don't get cocky now, Ye Li.

09:24.864 --> 09:27.504
Your Highness,
have you enjoyed what you watched?

09:28.504 --> 09:30.423
What makes you think I enjoy it?

09:32.624 --> 09:34.224
I'm your wife.

09:34.663 --> 09:37.823
Your Highness,
how could you not defend me just now?

09:39.104 --> 09:40.903
It's not that I didn't want to help,

09:41.504 --> 09:44.423
but your intricate ties
to everyone involved

09:44.663 --> 09:48.063
make things very complex.

09:48.663 --> 09:51.663
I want to help,
but there is nothing I can do.

09:53.104 --> 09:54.663
You truly want to help, Your Highness?

09:55.344 --> 09:56.144
Of course.

09:58.504 --> 10:00.384
You're quite suspicious, Your Highness.

10:01.264 --> 10:04.303
Since you think so, I won't pretend.

10:05.504 --> 10:08.264
Shouldn't you visit Prince Li
since he's wounded?

10:09.104 --> 10:10.384
Why should I care?

10:10.504 --> 10:11.624
What concern is it of mine?

10:13.583 --> 10:14.384
Let's go.

10:15.183 --> 10:16.464
Please hold, Princess Ding.

10:23.183 --> 10:25.104
You left something in Anqing Palace.

10:25.104 --> 10:27.024
Shall you return?

10:44.783 --> 10:46.984
Your grandfather and tutors
compose books.

10:47.543 --> 10:50.984
What do their students do then?

10:51.384 --> 10:52.423
Reading, writing,

10:53.264 --> 10:54.303
farming, hunting,

10:54.624 --> 10:56.984
drinking plum wine and tea

10:57.423 --> 10:58.423
at leisure.

10:58.663 --> 11:00.384
They pick tea leaves every early spring.

11:00.423 --> 11:02.943
My grandfather made poetry about it.

11:03.624 --> 11:05.624
Tea making takes both patience
and perfect skills.

11:05.903 --> 11:07.783
It's also a process
of finding inner peace.

11:11.984 --> 11:15.744
Really? Finding inner peace?

11:16.943 --> 11:22.104
Do they actually aim to live
as hermits forever?

11:23.703 --> 11:25.104
Some scholars

11:25.984 --> 11:28.024
used to live in seclusion.

11:28.423 --> 11:31.224
That's what our tutors want too.

11:31.624 --> 11:35.423
It's lucky for them
to live a quiet life on the mountain.

11:42.144 --> 11:44.744
I've studied Master Liu's calligraphy
for 20 years,

11:45.543 --> 11:48.583
but I still can't do it well.

11:52.183 --> 11:55.344
Do you know which sentence matters most

11:55.543 --> 11:57.104
in his work, Ode to Self-Cultivation?

11:59.024 --> 12:01.783
Utmost sincerity works wonders.

12:02.823 --> 12:04.583
You're clever,

12:05.104 --> 12:07.583
so you should know what I mean.

12:10.344 --> 12:12.423
Yes, I do.

12:13.384 --> 12:18.423
My grandfather taught me
that utmost sincerity makes good things.

12:18.783 --> 12:21.823
I always follow his teachings.

12:22.423 --> 12:26.183
Your Majesty, I want to say something

12:26.423 --> 12:28.703
my grandfather
and tutors never taught me.

12:28.823 --> 12:31.384
I'm very happy about my marriage.

12:32.183 --> 12:35.104
I'm grateful for your arrangement
and for freeing me from the mountain.

12:35.423 --> 12:37.224
I love my current life.

12:38.543 --> 12:42.423
What about your mother?
Is she also happy about your marriage?

12:47.423 --> 12:48.303
Your Majesty.

12:49.703 --> 12:50.583
My mom

12:51.624 --> 12:52.823
has passed away.

12:57.144 --> 12:58.104
What?

12:59.224 --> 13:00.024
Yes.

13:01.144 --> 13:03.024
She fell seriously ill on the way back

13:03.423 --> 13:06.624
and passed away
before reaching Lishan Mountain.

13:21.104 --> 13:22.344
(What about your mother?)

13:22.984 --> 13:24.984
(Is she also happy about your marriage?)

13:25.624 --> 13:26.504
(Your Majesty.)

13:27.903 --> 13:28.943
(My mom)

13:29.823 --> 13:31.024
(has passed away.)

13:39.783 --> 13:41.744
(She fell seriously ill on the way back)

13:42.024 --> 13:45.303
(and passed away
before reaching Lishan Mountain.)

14:08.583 --> 14:09.943
Your Highness, have you rested?

14:19.144 --> 14:19.744
Your Highness.

14:21.224 --> 14:22.303
Your hand is wounded.

14:22.624 --> 14:23.864
Let me treat it.

14:38.024 --> 14:42.063
You love music,
but you shouldn't value it over your body.

14:43.504 --> 14:47.464
And it takes time to compose a piece
in particular.

14:47.864 --> 14:49.224
Be patient, Your Highness.

14:51.744 --> 14:52.663
You think

14:53.744 --> 14:55.224
I'm upset about composing?

14:56.583 --> 14:57.264
What else?

14:59.543 --> 15:00.624
Please, Your Highness.

15:01.144 --> 15:03.504
If your hand is injured,
you can't play guqin anymore.

15:03.823 --> 15:06.423
Also, you can't compose new tunes
any time soon.

15:13.303 --> 15:17.063
Does your father
only have you and Ye Li?

15:18.744 --> 15:19.864
Sure, two daughters.

15:20.183 --> 15:21.344
But I have a younger brother.

15:21.624 --> 15:23.984
He's my biological brother, very clever.

15:24.183 --> 15:27.144
By the age of five, he'd read Mencius
and The Analects of Confucius.

15:27.744 --> 15:31.224
Even our family tutor praised him
as a rare prodigy.

15:31.903 --> 15:34.384
Did you grow up with Ye Li?

15:34.903 --> 15:37.144
I grew up with my younger brother.

15:37.903 --> 15:40.984
Ye Li lived at our house
before she turned 13.

15:41.624 --> 15:43.384
Although we were close in age,

15:43.744 --> 15:46.104
she often traveled
to Lishan with her mother,

15:46.504 --> 15:48.144
so we weren't particularly close.

15:49.384 --> 15:50.543
Do you remember things

15:50.703 --> 15:52.984
from your childhood?

15:54.583 --> 15:56.183
That was long ago.

15:56.823 --> 16:00.144
Nothing special. It's hardly memorable.

16:03.144 --> 16:05.504
Oh, I recall one incident.

16:05.943 --> 16:08.903
One year, we spent months together
in Hangzhou.

16:09.384 --> 16:11.464
The weather was quite hot.

16:11.624 --> 16:14.543
We decided to charter a boat
to pick lotus roots in the lake.

16:14.984 --> 16:17.344
Enormous red carp swam beneath!

16:17.504 --> 16:19.543
Like this big!

16:19.783 --> 16:21.703
Both Ye Li and I leaned over to see,

16:21.943 --> 16:23.504
but the boat rocked violently.

16:23.504 --> 16:25.663
I accidentally bumped into her,

16:26.024 --> 16:28.943
and she tumbled right into the lake.

16:30.344 --> 16:31.384
Such a ridiculous sight.

16:31.583 --> 16:33.783
She bobbed like a duck on the surface.

16:34.104 --> 16:36.464
She persistently demanded
an apology though.

16:36.864 --> 16:38.543
Why should I apologize?

16:39.024 --> 16:40.264
Guess what happened next?

16:40.703 --> 16:44.183
That silly girl swam straight across
and climbed out herself!

16:45.624 --> 16:47.583
She caught a chill afterward,

16:51.663 --> 16:53.224
sneezing endlessly.

16:59.663 --> 17:01.224
Oh, one more thing.

17:01.224 --> 17:02.864
On a rainy day like this,

17:03.423 --> 17:05.783
she suddenly grabbed me
and dashed outside.

17:05.863 --> 17:07.464
We kept running in the rain,

17:08.103 --> 17:11.383
and for no reason,
she burst into laughter.

17:11.383 --> 17:12.704
She was laughing very hard.

17:13.224 --> 17:15.583
I fell terribly ill after that.

17:15.904 --> 17:16.984
What a madwoman!

17:21.103 --> 17:22.543
Such heavy rain.

17:44.343 --> 17:45.143
Your Highness.

17:47.103 --> 17:49.224
Where did you get that shovel?

17:49.543 --> 17:50.863
I found it in the storage room.

17:51.264 --> 17:52.303
Do we have a saw?

17:52.424 --> 17:53.504
Probably.

17:53.623 --> 17:54.783
You need a saw?

17:55.024 --> 17:56.343
Leave one in the yard.

17:56.504 --> 17:57.264
All right.

18:54.583 --> 18:57.143
Your Highness,
she's going towards the backyard.

19:16.264 --> 19:19.303
Your Highness,
where exactly is she going so late?

19:19.583 --> 19:21.143
She has tools in her hand.

19:28.704 --> 19:29.904
Have Anyi follow her.

19:31.184 --> 19:31.984
Everything's ready.

19:32.224 --> 19:32.744
Let's go.

19:49.383 --> 19:50.504
Seems everyone's asleep.

19:53.424 --> 19:56.504
My lady, can we do this?

19:57.783 --> 20:00.704
Minghui entrusted this task to me
before I left the mountain.

20:01.264 --> 20:02.464
You keep watch here.

20:24.464 --> 20:25.264
Your Highness.

20:26.504 --> 20:29.583
Why did she come to this place so late?

20:48.704 --> 20:51.944
Your Highness, she is...

20:57.024 --> 20:57.704
Stealing a tree?

21:39.783 --> 21:40.343
Who's there?

21:41.024 --> 21:42.024
Father, wake up!

21:43.184 --> 21:43.984
Who's there?

21:43.984 --> 21:45.343
Look, Your Highness, well...

21:45.823 --> 21:46.944
Get up and check it out.

21:52.623 --> 21:53.296
Your Highness?

21:53.783 --> 21:54.583
Get in.

21:56.224 --> 21:56.944
Who is it?

21:57.143 --> 21:57.664
Tree thief!

21:57.664 --> 21:58.704
- Father, come on!
- Stop!

21:59.184 --> 21:59.823
Come on, Father.

22:03.424 --> 22:04.303
Ye Li.

22:29.583 --> 22:31.904
Speak. What were you doing?

22:34.863 --> 22:36.424
Can we talk in private?

22:36.583 --> 22:37.944
Now you feel embarrassed?

22:38.383 --> 22:40.704
In the dead of night,
you didn't sleep but stole trees

22:40.944 --> 22:42.583
from someone else's house?

22:43.664 --> 22:44.823
I never stole trees.

22:44.823 --> 22:45.823
How dare you deny it!

22:46.863 --> 22:47.944
What were you doing then?

22:50.063 --> 22:51.664
I just cut down a tree.

22:52.704 --> 22:55.863
Our mansion is full of trees.
Why did it have to be that one?

23:06.944 --> 23:07.783
Why cut down a tree?

23:10.744 --> 23:11.343
Explain!

23:19.583 --> 23:22.024
I know a man surnamed He
in Lishan Academy.

23:22.543 --> 23:23.543
He studies the Zhouyi.

23:24.184 --> 23:27.063
He failed imperial examinations twice.

23:27.424 --> 23:29.264
After divining his own fortune,

23:30.024 --> 23:34.583
he concluded the ginkgo tree
in front of his house ruined his luck.

23:34.704 --> 23:35.783
That's why he failed.

23:36.143 --> 23:39.343
Master Zhu insists his poor scholarship

23:39.383 --> 23:42.583
and laziness failed him, not a tree.

23:42.704 --> 23:44.143
He asked him to drop such thoughts.

23:44.583 --> 23:47.704
But the more Minghui is told
not to do this,

23:47.783 --> 23:49.823
the more he can't
stop thinking about it.

23:49.904 --> 23:51.744
Eventually, it became his obsession.

23:51.863 --> 23:53.504
He told me over and over

23:53.504 --> 23:55.103
to chop that tree down

23:55.143 --> 23:57.343
when I come down the mountain.

23:57.464 --> 24:00.264
When he once tried to chop that tree
and swung his axe just once,

24:00.583 --> 24:02.504
his father almost beat him to death.

24:05.184 --> 24:08.143
Then you should feel lucky
you just ran fast enough.

24:08.504 --> 24:09.823
That's because I run every day.

24:18.984 --> 24:20.783
Come on. Don't be angry.

24:29.944 --> 24:30.783
Never do it again.

24:35.823 --> 24:37.224
Why do you run every day?

24:37.944 --> 24:41.224
Your habit is different from others'.

24:44.264 --> 24:47.143
For health. I have to stay active.

24:47.664 --> 24:49.744
And I also hope I can run faster.

24:49.944 --> 24:51.103
Run faster? Why?

24:54.143 --> 24:55.303
Li! Come back!

24:57.264 --> 24:58.024
Li!

25:02.424 --> 25:03.184
Li!

25:04.264 --> 25:05.024
Go that way!

25:06.664 --> 25:07.424
Li!

25:11.744 --> 25:12.583
Li!

25:12.583 --> 25:13.264
- You can't leave.
- Help!

25:13.264 --> 25:14.504
- Do not give in to them!
- Help!

25:14.504 --> 25:15.704
- Li!
- Let go of me!

25:15.704 --> 25:16.823
I don't want to hurt you.

25:16.823 --> 25:17.863
But you can't leave.

25:17.944 --> 25:19.264
Master Helai will find a way. Go.

25:19.264 --> 25:19.783
Let go!

25:19.783 --> 25:20.303
Go!

25:23.664 --> 25:26.143
Anyway, I promise it won't happen again.

25:44.984 --> 25:46.464
Where have you been?

25:46.464 --> 25:49.024
I asked you to keep watch,
and I ended up cornered!

25:49.383 --> 25:51.504
His Highness even caught up,
and you didn't show up.

25:52.664 --> 25:54.184
I intended to remind you.

25:54.823 --> 25:57.464
But when I saw His Highness coming,

25:57.783 --> 25:59.303
I got scared and stayed quiet.

26:02.343 --> 26:03.504
Such a coward!

26:05.623 --> 26:06.823
It won't happen again.

26:28.783 --> 26:31.783
Come on. Playing his guqin
in the morning again.

26:32.744 --> 26:35.224
He treats that piece of wood
like treasure.

26:45.063 --> 26:48.623
Ma'am, he hasn't given me
a proper look for days!

26:50.063 --> 26:53.184
If His Highness detests me,
what should I do?

26:53.583 --> 26:55.863
I know an animal trainer
from the Western Regions.

26:56.184 --> 26:59.143
He controls a phoenix with music.
Absolutely stunning.

26:59.383 --> 27:02.383
I'll go ask him to teach you that.

27:02.783 --> 27:04.184
His Highness loves music.

27:04.783 --> 27:07.823
Seeing your sincere effort to learn,
he'll surely be touched.

27:09.224 --> 27:09.724
Alright.

27:21.264 --> 27:22.744
Stop squinting at me.

27:23.063 --> 27:24.863
Just look directly at me.

27:28.823 --> 27:29.623
Your Highness.

27:30.424 --> 27:33.783
Did His Highness scold you
for sealing a tree yesterday?

27:35.863 --> 27:36.744
How did you know?

27:37.944 --> 27:39.823
I overheard it earlier.

27:41.944 --> 27:42.744
No.

27:43.143 --> 27:45.264
He didn't scold me,
nor did I steal a tree.

27:45.264 --> 27:46.303
You misheard.

27:49.583 --> 27:51.424
Your Highness, a report from outside.

27:51.424 --> 27:52.783
An elderly man wishes to see you.

27:54.863 --> 27:57.424
I'm He Jin. Greetings, Your Highness.

27:58.143 --> 27:58.944
Please, have a seat.

28:02.583 --> 28:05.024
I am the father of He Minghui.

28:05.303 --> 28:07.583
My son is currently studying
at Lishan Academy.

28:07.583 --> 28:10.783
I think you know him. He's your senior.

28:12.543 --> 28:13.343
Yes, Mr. He.

28:14.863 --> 28:17.823
I came today for one thing.

28:18.303 --> 28:21.783
Last night, a tree at my home
was inexplicably chopped down.

28:21.904 --> 28:25.383
May I ask if Your Highness
sent someone to do that?

28:30.583 --> 28:34.024
I am not here to blame,
merely to find out why.

28:34.744 --> 28:37.664
For these eight years,
Minghui has sent no word.

28:37.664 --> 28:39.264
But after that tree fell,

28:39.623 --> 28:43.024
I began to think if he had returned.

28:43.984 --> 28:48.383
Yet upon inquiring, I learned
Lishan Mountain is not open yet.

28:48.383 --> 28:50.264
You're the only one
who left the mountain.

28:50.424 --> 28:51.984
So I guess

28:52.783 --> 28:55.944
Minghui asked you to chop it down.

28:58.424 --> 29:01.783
Minghui indeed asked me to cut it down.

29:02.264 --> 29:05.424
I did it secretly,
fearing your disapproval.

29:06.504 --> 29:07.664
Please forgive me.

29:07.744 --> 29:09.184
It doesn't matter.

29:09.504 --> 29:10.504
Sit, please.

29:13.504 --> 29:15.623
How is he doing up on the mountain?

29:16.024 --> 29:18.303
Is he living a good life?

29:18.904 --> 29:19.944
Don't worry.

29:20.424 --> 29:23.464
The academy cultivates its own land
to grow vegetables.

29:23.823 --> 29:25.143
Wild fruits grow in the forest.

29:25.184 --> 29:26.343
Food is quite sufficient.

29:27.464 --> 29:30.224
Oh, he has even learned
to make sesame cakes himself.

29:30.264 --> 29:31.744
He can eat three whole ones.

29:31.984 --> 29:35.063
Good for him. He's loved sesame cakes
since he was little.

29:39.904 --> 29:40.984
Excuse me for this.

29:41.623 --> 29:43.944
How does he get along with the tutors?

29:44.303 --> 29:48.543
After so many years,
has he become better academically?

29:49.583 --> 29:51.904
He is smart and diligent.

29:52.024 --> 29:54.103
He frequently earns praise
from the tutors.

29:54.103 --> 29:56.143
That's good! Very good!

29:57.303 --> 30:01.024
Minghui is always clever
and studies hard.

30:01.224 --> 30:02.543
But he never listened to me.

30:03.224 --> 30:05.823
Back then, I wanted him to marry early.

30:05.823 --> 30:07.383
But he flat-out refused,

30:07.583 --> 30:09.863
packed his bags,
and went off to Lishan Mountain.

30:10.783 --> 30:12.184
He didn't even come home.

30:13.024 --> 30:15.904
It's been eight years.

30:16.383 --> 30:20.623
Now he's 32, yet still unmarried.

30:22.424 --> 30:24.583
It's truly nerve-wracking!

30:27.303 --> 30:29.783
Oh, well. To each their own,

30:30.264 --> 30:33.224
as long as he believes
he's doing what's right.

30:35.063 --> 30:39.464
Many spend their entire lives
unsure of what is truly right.

30:42.143 --> 30:45.303
Your Highness,
when will you return to Lishan Mountain?

30:46.543 --> 30:48.664
It's unlikely to happen soon.

30:50.264 --> 30:50.783
I see.

30:54.904 --> 30:57.024
I wrote a letter.

30:57.424 --> 30:59.783
Would it be possible
to pass it along to Minghui?

31:00.783 --> 31:01.783
Certainly, no problem.

31:02.623 --> 31:05.143
I write to tutors regularly.

31:05.224 --> 31:06.424
I'll pass it to him for you.

31:06.543 --> 31:07.343
Really?

31:07.783 --> 31:09.424
That's wonderful!

31:10.303 --> 31:13.024
Thank you, Your Highness.

31:13.623 --> 31:14.623
Please take care, Mr. He.

31:27.664 --> 31:28.976
(To He Minghui)

31:41.264 --> 31:47.180
(Prince Li's Mansion)

31:54.224 --> 31:56.504
Her Highness has been waiting. Come in.

31:58.143 --> 31:59.343
Make its feathers nice.

31:59.583 --> 32:00.383
Is this good?

32:00.583 --> 32:02.103
No. Make it nicer.

32:02.103 --> 32:02.783
Ma'am.

32:02.783 --> 32:03.283
Hurry!

32:03.424 --> 32:05.063
This is the phoenix you mentioned?

32:05.543 --> 32:07.063
But it's clearly a peacock!

32:07.704 --> 32:09.103
You think His Highness likes this?

32:09.823 --> 32:11.424
Please, Your Highness.

32:11.504 --> 32:13.143
Real phoenixes don't exist.

32:13.343 --> 32:15.863
The peacock is stunning already.

32:16.424 --> 32:18.024
Look at its gorgeous tail.

32:18.464 --> 32:21.024
It complements your elegant grace.

32:25.264 --> 32:26.103
Your Highness.

32:26.303 --> 32:28.504
This peacock is incredibly intelligent.

32:28.623 --> 32:31.984
Play this flute
following the tune I teach,

32:31.984 --> 32:33.904
and it will open its feathers and fly.

32:34.103 --> 32:36.063
The melody is called Bird Summoning.

33:07.264 --> 33:08.264
Look, Your Highness.

33:08.823 --> 33:10.264
It's so beautiful!

33:11.264 --> 33:14.744
Mastering this will surely
please His Highness.

33:18.264 --> 33:19.664
Quickly, teach me this!

33:19.744 --> 33:20.244
Yes.

33:24.464 --> 33:25.383
Observe, Your Highness.

33:26.063 --> 33:28.543
This flute has seven finger holes.

33:29.103 --> 33:32.543
Proper finger placement is critical.

33:33.103 --> 33:36.264
Cover this hole with your thumb.

33:38.184 --> 33:38.984
Yes.

33:39.103 --> 33:45.264
Then, cover the second and fourth holes
with your index finger and ring finger.

33:45.863 --> 33:47.823
Good, just like that.

33:48.103 --> 33:51.303
Inhale deeply, and then try blowing.

33:57.783 --> 33:59.024
How could it sound so dreadful?

33:59.303 --> 34:00.704
Are you mocking me?

34:00.863 --> 34:01.664
No, I'm not.

34:01.863 --> 34:05.143
Perhaps your finger placement and breath
weren't synchronized.

34:05.504 --> 34:07.543
The art of music requires patience.

34:07.623 --> 34:08.583
Do not rush.

34:09.103 --> 34:11.984
Master the breath control as you play.

34:12.543 --> 34:15.063
I'll try now and make them fly.

34:46.183 --> 34:47.024
Come on.

34:47.583 --> 34:48.824
Hello, Li.

34:51.024 --> 34:53.944
Where did you go? You seem worn out.

34:54.223 --> 34:56.743
Even criminals look more decent
than you now.

34:56.944 --> 34:57.504
Well,

34:57.984 --> 35:00.103
I went to a place
30 li away from the city

35:00.623 --> 35:04.424
to inspect terracotta figurines shipped
from Datong Prefecture.

35:04.424 --> 35:05.103
And?

35:05.223 --> 35:06.063
Not good.

35:06.103 --> 35:09.304
Even worse quality
than the last painted pottery.

35:10.464 --> 35:12.103
So you went there for nothing.

35:13.183 --> 35:13.984
Not really.

35:15.063 --> 35:17.263
On my return, just at the city gate,

35:17.344 --> 35:18.784
I witnessed a strange thing.

35:19.464 --> 35:20.504
What happened?

35:20.623 --> 35:24.543
A caravan from the Western Regions
brought blue peacocks the other day.

35:24.864 --> 35:27.143
Their show attracted big crowds.

35:27.344 --> 35:29.824
But today, they'd barely begun

35:30.143 --> 35:32.024
when Prince Li's carriage rolled up.

35:32.344 --> 35:34.703
They took away the performer
and the birds.

35:35.344 --> 35:39.864
I heard they invited
the famous animal trainer

35:40.344 --> 35:42.984
to learn how to tame birds.

35:43.743 --> 35:45.904
Does Princess Li want to learn?

35:47.743 --> 35:50.464
Ye Ying has always been very impatient.

35:50.824 --> 35:54.024
I'd rather believe the trainer can fly
than that she can learn.

35:56.623 --> 35:57.583
Here's the account book.

35:57.864 --> 35:59.263
I've watched the shop for a while.

35:59.263 --> 36:00.344
I'm heading home.

36:00.424 --> 36:01.304
Thank you.

36:05.143 --> 36:06.543
No deals. No...

36:06.623 --> 36:08.824
Why did you record this?

36:09.063 --> 36:12.504
Your Highness, I forgot to buy cakes.

36:13.263 --> 36:14.223
Go ahead.

36:14.984 --> 36:16.143
The carriage is over there.

36:16.263 --> 36:17.623
You return first.

36:21.223 --> 36:22.143
Mo Wuyou! Stop!

36:22.143 --> 36:22.784
Stop!

36:23.504 --> 36:24.944
Mo Wuyou, stop right there!

36:25.623 --> 36:26.304
Stop!

36:26.304 --> 36:26.904
Mo Wuyou!

36:26.904 --> 36:27.583
Stop!

36:27.784 --> 36:28.384
Mo Wuyou!

36:28.424 --> 36:28.984
Halt!

36:28.984 --> 36:29.583
Don't you run!

36:29.703 --> 36:30.743
Stop!

36:43.143 --> 36:44.464
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

36:45.223 --> 36:46.143
Are you okay?

36:47.464 --> 36:48.464
I just don't believe it!

36:51.663 --> 36:52.824
Mo Wuyou, stop right there!

36:54.183 --> 36:54.824
I caught you.

36:54.824 --> 36:55.623
You can't run away.

36:55.784 --> 36:56.304
I caught you.

36:56.304 --> 36:56.804
Caught you.

37:06.344 --> 37:06.844
Beat him!

37:11.703 --> 37:12.384
Be careful!

37:12.384 --> 37:13.063
Your Highness.

37:13.344 --> 37:14.964
Be careful, Your Highness.

37:15.344 --> 37:15.904
Watch out!

37:15.904 --> 37:16.984
Get them!

37:17.143 --> 37:17.944
Yes!

37:20.183 --> 37:21.143
No fighting!

37:27.543 --> 37:28.223
Run!

37:28.464 --> 37:29.304
Get out of here!

37:30.623 --> 37:31.304
Wuyou!

37:31.543 --> 37:32.944
Stop fighting, Wuyou!

37:34.743 --> 37:35.784
Get home right now!

37:49.904 --> 37:51.944
If they don't fly, I'll make you fly!

37:53.543 --> 37:55.743
Your Highness,
time to prepare your dinner.

37:55.743 --> 37:57.464
I'd like to fly first.

37:57.464 --> 37:58.143
You...

38:00.864 --> 38:01.424
Ma'am.

38:01.424 --> 38:02.263
I'll fly with you!

38:02.263 --> 38:03.143
I'm flying too!

38:06.143 --> 38:08.304
Your Highness, I really can't fly!

38:12.384 --> 38:14.984
Those kids don't seem very big.

38:15.223 --> 38:16.464
But they hit you hard.

38:18.864 --> 38:20.344
Why were they hitting you?

38:20.623 --> 38:23.703
Did you tell them you're a Young Lord?

38:25.583 --> 38:26.663
None of your business.

38:28.864 --> 38:29.623
Who are they?

38:30.784 --> 38:32.784
Classmates. Happy now?

38:40.944 --> 38:43.703
Saying nothing doesn't make you tough.

38:44.464 --> 38:46.663
It doesn't mean
you've solved your problems.

38:49.784 --> 38:52.504
Mo Wuyou, you're still a child.

38:53.504 --> 38:55.504
When a gang of kids was punching you,

38:55.504 --> 38:56.543
you didn't back down.

38:57.464 --> 38:58.703
Very brave of you.

38:59.623 --> 39:02.583
But if you share your troubles
with your family,

39:03.063 --> 39:04.904
it also means you're brave.

39:06.063 --> 39:08.944
You know why they hit me?

39:12.623 --> 39:13.743
I can probably guess.

39:14.784 --> 39:17.784
But troublemakers
will always find a pretext for trouble.

39:18.263 --> 39:19.944
Because trouble is all they are.

39:20.344 --> 39:21.743
Kids cause trouble and get beaten,

39:21.824 --> 39:23.143
while adults end up in jail.

39:27.623 --> 39:29.183
Don't get tangled with them.

39:31.864 --> 39:33.384
And don't let them soil you.

39:35.183 --> 39:36.583
They aren't worth your time.

39:41.103 --> 39:41.904
Ma'am.

39:42.504 --> 39:45.583
Why do you think
I just can't make the peacock fly?

39:47.583 --> 39:48.384
Your Highness.

39:49.143 --> 39:51.784
Not everything is done on the first try.

39:51.864 --> 39:53.063
Just be patient.

39:54.784 --> 39:56.384
Eat something, okay?

39:58.784 --> 39:59.583
I won't eat.

40:01.384 --> 40:02.583
I must master it.

40:04.784 --> 40:05.583
Your Highness.

40:36.424 --> 40:37.223
Ding.

40:38.143 --> 40:39.344
What makes you so happy?

40:39.784 --> 40:41.824
Good news, Your Highness.

40:41.864 --> 40:43.384
His Highness received an appointment!

40:43.384 --> 40:45.424
He'll soon go take office
at Jingzhao Prefecture.

41:10.623 --> 41:11.424
Your Highness.

41:15.304 --> 41:18.063
Where have you been?
Why are you back so late?

41:19.784 --> 41:21.143
I went to watch the shop.

41:24.623 --> 41:26.143
Plenty of mud on your shoes.

41:28.424 --> 41:29.223
How?

41:30.183 --> 41:33.063
Is the path from the mansion
to Shende Shop that muddy?

41:41.663 --> 41:43.223
I helped Wuyou with a fight.

41:43.864 --> 41:46.424
On my way home,
I saw a bunch of kids bullying him.

41:46.944 --> 41:49.063
I couldn't pull them apart,
so I jumped in to help.

41:53.063 --> 41:54.464
You shouldn't doubt me.

41:54.984 --> 41:57.464
You should ask me who bullied him

41:57.543 --> 41:58.944
and help him get even.

42:01.944 --> 42:03.743
Kids always fight. It's normal.

42:04.944 --> 42:07.944
It's normal that one group of kids
fights another group.

42:08.063 --> 42:10.344
But Wuyou alone
was being beaten up by a group.

42:10.344 --> 42:11.583
That isn't normal.

42:14.944 --> 42:16.263
His father is gone.

42:16.304 --> 42:19.784
You are his uncle,
so you must protect him.

42:19.904 --> 42:22.663
He's a Young Lord,

42:22.784 --> 42:24.944
yet he doesn't even
have a page boy beside him.

42:25.304 --> 42:28.344
Nobody else knows he got injured.
Is that right?

42:30.583 --> 42:31.424
I see.

42:40.208 --> 42:42.800
(Preview)

42:43.424 --> 42:47.183
I really, really want
to see him one more time.

42:47.663 --> 42:49.824
Even in my dreams.

42:50.784 --> 42:54.223
Greetings from the 27 innocent souls
of your clan

42:54.824 --> 42:55.703
received.

42:57.143 --> 42:59.504
You're most likely to get mouth sores.

43:00.223 --> 43:01.743
Let me heal your legs.

43:01.864 --> 43:03.743
It can wait.

43:04.103 --> 43:05.103
Where did Monkey go?

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
